	<name>Sticky</name>
	<summary>Simple sticky notes for your desktop</summary>
	<description>
		<p>
			Create and edit sticky notes mindful of the Elementary OS color scheme.

			Quit and save your notes any time with Ctrl+Q.
		</p>
		<p>
			Features Include:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Custom colors</li>
			<li>Pin above other windows</li>
			<li>Text formatting</li>
		</ul>
	</description>
